ZH: 今天晚上我要去朋友家作客。
EN: Tonight I am going to visit my friend's house.

ZH: 他们家里不怎么经常有人作客。
EN: They don't have guests over very often.

ZH: 昨天我在一家很热情的餐馆作客。
EN: Yesterday I dined at a very welcoming restaurant.

ZH: 这个周末我们计划作客去爷爷奶奶家。
EN: This weekend we plan to visit my grandparents.

ZH: 作客他们家的时候，我感到非常舒适。
EN: When I'm a guest at their house, I feel very comfortable.

ZH: 我们非常欢迎你在我们家作客。
EN: We are very welcoming to have you as a guest in our home.

ZH: 老师的一位朋友作客去了我们学校。
EN: One of the teacher's friends visited our school as a guest.

ZH: 最近我每个周末都在外地作客。
EN: Lately, I've been visiting different places every weekend.

ZH: 当他作客时，他总是带一份小礼物。
EN: Whenever he visits, he always brings a small gift.

ZH: 我们一起作客在一个玛奇朵的音乐会上。
EN: We were guests together at a Macciato concert.

ZH: 他把我们当作客人一样招待。
EN: He treated us as guests.

ZH: 爷爷奶奶很高兴我经常作客去他们家。
EN: My grandparents are delighted that I frequently visit their home.

ZH: 作客肯定要注意礼节。
EN: When you are a guest, it is important to mind your manners.

ZH: 作客的时候，我们要尊重主人的规矩。
EN: When visiting as a guest, it is important to respect the host's rules.

ZH: 我们作客他们家的时候，他们总是对我们很热情。
EN: When we visit their house as guests, they are always very welcoming.

ZH: 作客的时候，我喜欢闲聊和主人聊天。
EN: When I am a guest, I enjoy chatting and talking with the host.

ZH: 我喜欢作客朋友家，因为他们总是有好吃的食物。
EN: I enjoy visiting my friend's house because they always have delicious food.

ZH: 作客的时候，我们可以品尝不同的菜肴。
EN: When we are guests, we can try different dishes.

ZH: 当他作客来我家时，我总是提供他他最喜欢的茶。
EN: When he visits my house, I always offer him his favorite tea.

ZH: 我邀请他作客，因为他是我的好朋友。
EN: I invited him as a guest because he is my good friend.
